strings.Value: "Today our camp sits in plain view. We might get uninvited guests. Got it? Don't walk around your tents naked, ha ha ha!"
"You didn't disguise the camp tonight? Well, if you hear any scary sounds — don't just assume it's me having fun in my tent. It might be some kind of beast."
[Rolls her eyes with a deep sigh]
"There's nothing to be afraid of. Any enemy who sees you naked will run for the hills — and never look back!"
